sub_title: Advisor at the Norwegian Delegation to the UN organisations in Rome
summary:
I would define myself as: optimistic, reliable, caring, and empathetic.

My passions are sustainable development, gender and migration policies, and climate justice. I am eager to engage with policymakers, INGOs, academia, and civil society. I am thrilled to strengthen my policy research, project management, and partnership development abilities. 

I have expertise in policy analysis, partnership development, data collection & analysis, and project management. I master different research methodologies: quant & qual data collection (surveys, interviews) and data analysis (Atlas-ti, Excel), case studies, policy analysis, and literature reviews.

I am fluent in Italian (C2), English (C2), Danish (C1), Spanish (C1), Portuguese (B2), and learning Dutch (A2/B1).
